  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IFXGNode, IPreserveWhiteSpaceNode, ITextNode

    public class ParagraphNode
extends AbstractRichParagraphNode
    Represents a <p /> child tag of FXG <RichText> content. A <p> tag starts a new paragraph in text content.

      • addChild

        public void addChild(IFXGNode child,
            Collection<ICompilerProblem> problems)
        Adds an FXG child node to this Paragraph node. Supported child nodes include text content nodes (e.g. tcy, a, span, tab, br, and img). Note that link format nodes (e.g. linkNormalFormat, linkHoverFormat, and linkActiveFormat) are complex properties rather than child nodes.
